props.name: text
props.description: Text for the navigation link item. If content is provided in the default slot, this prop will be ignored.

props.name: href
props.description: Href attribute for the navigation link item.

props.name: component
props.description: The component used to render the link, for example `RouterLink`.

slots.name: default
slots.description: The content of the navigation link. If content is provided in this slot, the `text` prop will be ignored.
